"2018-04-05T05:10:28.000Z","msg":"2個人住呢"},{"pid":"8102d59c4504a08bb4be20b9c1fb9fb1c7c2aa42","tid":614812,"uid":62554,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T05:30:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>清境有三間古堡式民宿，老英格蘭，音樂，空中花園<br />\n住過音樂古堡，千幾蚊晚有兩層，夠4個人住，又有hi fi ，包早餐，包車<br />\n酒店內外都幾有feel <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>2個人住呢</blockquote><br />\n一張大床，兩張單人床<br />\n如果同條女去，影相夠影一晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n反正夜晚6點後都無野做，影下女神相，可以呃下like<br />\n兩個男人就算吧啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f356b1e481ae956fb8b77285e3700331f56a9744","tid":614812,"uid":125460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3be9eeb86df8293bb347a1ac5de8188ca2693d40","tid":614812,"uid":10520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38126cce5bce0af9d125208d4f543d357aed02ce","tid":614812,"uid":125460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T06:08:37.000Z","msg":"清境布格拉民宿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T15:11:55.000Z","msg":"點正法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T09:04:47.000Z","msg":"入面裝修靚，有露台睇到星"},{"pid":"9f3b02e0df2563495bda0425f0dfabc868f4940e","tid":614812,"uid":101759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T09:34:52.000Z","msg":"住過清境寞內花園山莊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好有feel有個細浴缸隔離窗口有山景睇<br />\n幾步路有7-11 同埋個度門口養左好多貓咪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}